This code always allow you to get in the boxes Light Items in any position that you are in the game. 
The item that you will get are: coins, banana, green shell, super horn and all items that the player
always obtained when are in the first place. This code also affects other players in the online game,
the code forces the server for other players to get the same items that you get. This only affects 
some players, especially when a race is among 10 or fewer players.

Replace Y's with your desired button activator to activate.
Replace Z's with your desired button activator to deactivate.

